      • getSkill

        @Pure
protected abstract def getSkill(capacity : Class<S>) : S  with <S extends Capacity>
        Description copied from class: AgentProtectedAPIObject
        Replies the skill corresponding to the given capacity.

        The return may never be null. If not capacity was set, the exception UnimplementedCapacityException is thrown.

        Type Parameters:
        S - - type of the capacity.
        Parameters:
        capacity - the capacity to search for the implementation.
        Returns:
        the skill, never null
        Throws:
        UnimplementedCapacityException - - if no skill is owned by the agent for the given capacity.
